Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.19,0:00:25.34,Default,,0,0,0,,September 21, 1945.\NThat was the night I died.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.29,0:00:58.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Disgusting.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.56,0:01:00.07,Default,,0,0,0,,- Hey, watch it!\N- Sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.66,0:01:02.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Is he dead?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.80,0:01:05.93,Default,,0,0,0,,The Americans'll be arriving\Nany day now.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.32,0:01:09.22,Default,,0,0,0,,These bums are a disgrace.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:17.96,0:01:19.88,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Mama...!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.42,0:01:24.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Tell me. What day is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.26,0:01:37.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Setsuko...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.52,0:01:49.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Another one.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.18,0:02:04.76,Default,,0,0,0,,What is this stuff?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.01,0:02:07.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, what does it matter?\NJust dump it!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.05,0:02:22.61,Default,,0,0,0,,This one's a goner, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.38,0:02:25.97,Default,,0,0,0,,You can see it in their eyes.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.33,0:04:55.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Air raid! Get to the shelters!\NQuickly!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.51,0:04:59.29,Default,,0,0,0,,We're in for a big\None this time!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.02,0:05:03.92,Default,,0,0,0,,The shelter behind the firehouse\Nshould be safest!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.22,0:05:09.52,Default,,0,0,0,,It's hot!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.63,0:05:12.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Be a good girl.\NTry to be patient.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.62,0:05:19.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, I guess I had better\Nget over to the shelter.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.36,0:05:23.17,Default,,0,0,0,,So be careful , Seita, and get\Nover there as soon as you can.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.13,0:05:27.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Setsuko, be a good girl\Nand listen to your brother.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.43,0:05:29.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Mom, never mind us!\NGet to the shelter!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.80,0:05:31.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.03,0:05:34.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Mom, do you have your medicine with you?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.51,0:05:36.52,Default,,0,0,0,,I have it right here.\NDon't worry.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.40,0:05:43.22,Default,,0,0,0,,I hate the shelter!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.35,0:05:45.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, you'll be sorry\Nif you get blown up by a bomb.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.02,0:05:46.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Now get on.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.01,0:05:56.46,Default,,0,0,0,,My doll! My doll!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.93,0:06:10.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Air raid!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.09,0:06:11.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Seita!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.59,0:06:25.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Get down!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.84,0:07:31.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Seita! Seita!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.71,0:07:44.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Seita!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.43,0:07:59.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Hurry! Let's go! Let's go!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.58,0:08:15.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Clear the way, people!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.87,0:08:17.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Move the damn cart, will you?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.69,0:08:32.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh god!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.02,0:08:50.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Take whatever you can carry.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.61,0:09:45.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Long live the Emperor!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.49,0:10:08.64,Default,,0,0,0,,We're safe here. Don't worry, OK.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.47,0:10:12.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Where's Mama? I want Mama.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.62,0:10:14.99,Default,,0,0,0,,She is in the shelter.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.26,0:10:20.65,Default,,0,0,0,,The firehouse shelter can take\Na hit from a 250-kilo bomb easy.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.81,0:10:21.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't worry about her.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.20,0:10:36.42,Default,,0,0,0,,She'll probably go to\NNiponmatsu station to find us.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.05,0:10:39.00,Default,,0,0,0,,When things calm down,\Nwe will meet her there.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.22,0:10:41.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's just rest a bit.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.95,0:10:50.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you okay, Setsuko?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.30,0:10:52.46,Default,,0,0,0,,I lost one of my shoes.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.36,0:10:57.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't worry. I'll\Nbuy better ones.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.41,0:11:00.67,Default,,0,0,0,,I have some money.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.94,0:11:09.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Open this.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.58,0:11:22.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Wow Setsuko, you're rich.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.88,0:11:34.17,Default,,0,0,0,,It's black rain, from\Nall of the bombing.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.49,0:12:15.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Look...\NIt's all gone!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.41,0:12:21.62,Default,,0,0,0,,That was the civic hall.\NWe ate lunch there, once.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.24,0:12:27.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Seita, Is our house gone too?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.96,0:12:29.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Probably.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.80,0:12:30.94,Default,,0,0,0,,What'll we do?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.15,0:12:34.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Dad'll make them pay for this!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.75,0:12:52.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Mother! Mother!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.12,0:13:05.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, it's not like I was\Nthe only one who lost his house.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.52,0:13:07.84,Default,,0,0,0,,We're all in the same boat.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.35,0:13:10.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, at least we're still alive.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.15,0:13:22.08,Default,,0,0,0,,There were two direct hits.\NThe fires are impossible to put out!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.12,0:13:24.89,Default,,0,0,0,,When you try to smother them,\Nit just spreads the oil around.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.41,0:13:28.56,Default,,0,0,0,,It's not her.\NShe's not down here!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.60,0:13:35.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Seita, I have to pee.\N- OK.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.12,0:13:51.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Attention all residents of\NIchirizuka and Kaminishi!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.45,0:13:56.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Please report to the elementary\Nschool for first aid services!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.02,0:13:57.64,Default,,0,0,0,,What's wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.95,0:13:59.55,Default,,0,0,0,,My eye hurts.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.66,0:14:00.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't rub it.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.72,0:14:04.14,Default,,0,0,0,,We'll get it washed out\Nat the school.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.16,0:14:06.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Where's Mama?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.11,0:14:08.08,Default,,0,0,0,,She'll be there.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.52,0:14:09.60,Default,,0,0,0,,At School...?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.64,0:14:11.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes. Let's go.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.31,0:14:30.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh Seita! Come with me.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.83,0:14:34.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Have you seen your mother yet?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.00,0:14:36.91,Default,,0,0,0,,She's been injured. Go to her.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.20,0:14:39.50,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll watch your sister.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.36,0:14:43.01,Default,,0,0,0,,My goodness. wasn't\Nthat scary, Setsuko?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.68,0:14:47.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Seita has to go somewhere.\NWe'll wait for him together.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.86,0:14:59.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Seita. I am glad you are here.\NAre you okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.02,0:15:00.52,Default,,0,0,0,,My mom...?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.63,0:15:01.20,Default,,0,0,0,,This way.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.92,0:15:13.02,Default,,0,0,0,,This is your mother's, isn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.61,0:15:17.21,Default,,0,0,0,,In here.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.72,0:15:30.55,Default,,0,0,0,,She's finally fallen asleep.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.49,0:15:39.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Your Mother really should be in a\Nproper hospital. We can't do much here.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.00,0:15:44.11,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't think they have hit\NKaisei hospital in Nishinomiya.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.52,0:15:50.06,Default,,0,0,0,,My mother-My mother has heart trouble.\NCan she get her medicine?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.34,0:15:52.25,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll find out.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.72,0:15:57.73,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll be around, son.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.42,0:16:04.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Mom, are you...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.36,0:16:27.18,Default,,0,0,0,,You saw her?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.46,0:16:28.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.50,0:16:30.09,Default,,0,0,0,,I am so sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.22,0:16:32.42,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm thirsty.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.73,0:16:40.24,Default,,0,0,0,,If there's anything I can do,\Njust ask.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.34,0:16:44.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Did you get your ration?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.72,0:16:46.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Let me. I'll get it for you!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.49,0:17:02.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Keep this ring safe in your purse.\NDon't lose it, OK?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.92,0:17:07.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Mom's been hurt, Setsuko.\NBut she'll get better soon.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.94,0:17:10.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Where is Mama?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.73,0:17:12.94,Default,,0,0,0,,In the hospital. In Nishinomiya.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.98,0:17:18.54,Default,,0,0,0,,We'll stay here\Nat the school tonight.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.73,0:17:23.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Then tomorrow, we'll go to stay at our\NAunt's house near the hospital, OK?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.42,0:17:25.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Setsuko?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.53,0:17:28.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Understand?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.10,0:17:42.98,Default,,0,0,0,,We're all staying on the second floor.\NWhy don't you stop by later?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.85,0:17:48.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you for all your kindness. We will.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.15,0:17:52.09,Default,,0,0,0,,See you later then. Bye now.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.27,0:17:56.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Want some?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.99,0:17:58.91,Default,,0,0,0,,I want to see Mama.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.71,0:18:03.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Maybe tomorrow.\NIt's too late now.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.53,0:18:58.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Setsuko, watch me, I'm good at this!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.73,0:19:27.55,Default,,0,0,0,,I haven't unbandaged her. Believe\Nme, you don't want to see the body.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.64,0:19:31.28,Default,,0,0,0,,With this heat we're having,\Nshe'll have to go on the truck today.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.86,0:19:48.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Where's your sister?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.42,0:19:52.60,Default,,0,0,0,,In Nishinomiya.\NWe have a distant aunt there.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.56,0:19:55.24,Default,,0,0,0,,I think she'll take care of us.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.88,0:19:58.16,Default,,0,0,0,,I see. Lucky for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.32,0:20:02.60,Default,,0,0,0,,I'd better get back to work.\NGood luck to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.71,0:21:31.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Mama!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.60,0:21:33.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Where is Mama?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.28,0:21:37.82,Default,,0,0,0,,What's the matter?\NIs she still sick?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.20,0:21:40.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah. Yeah, she is still sick.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.60,0:21:41.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Welcome back.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.12,0:21:46.80,Default,,0,0,0,,How's your mother?\NIs she at Kaisei?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.10,0:21:48.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.23,0:21:51.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Lucky your dad's in the Navy.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.13,0:21:54.13,Default,,0,0,0,,You get to have a truck\Nhelp move you over here!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.40,0:21:59.01,Default,,0,0,0,,I've laid out futons and\Nmosquito netting in your room.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.99,0:22:00.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:09.44,0:22:12.83,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't understand. Doesn't\NMama need her ring?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:13.87,0:22:16.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Did she give it to\Nme to keep for her?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:21.96,0:22:24.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Just be careful\Nyou don't lose it.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:31.66,0:22:32.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Setsuko...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:35.39,0:22:37.97,Default,,0,0,0,,When Mom's a little better,\NI'll take you to see her.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:40.51,0:22:41.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Time for bed. OK?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:36.44,0:24:42.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Dried bonito, herring, some\Ndried potato, pickled plums.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:44.13,0:24:46.52,Default,,0,0,0,,And I do believe this is butter!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:49.33,0:24:52.47,Default,,0,0,0,,All of these things are so\Nhard to come by nowadays.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:52.74,0:24:55.18,Default,,0,0,0,,It's soldiers' families\Nalways get the best.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:55.93,0:24:59.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Anyway, did you stop\Nby the hospital today?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:59.66,0:25:03.05,Default,,0,0,0,,I'd like to tell your mother all the\Nthings that have been happening.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:03.22,0:25:06.04,Default,,0,0,0,,And I could take Setsuko along\Nto visit her.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:09.12,0:25:10.10,Default,,0,0,0,,How bad?!
Dialogue: 0,0:25:10.93,0:25:13.36,Default,,0,0,0,,My Mom passed away while she\Nwas still at the school.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:13.99,0:25:16.36,Default,,0,0,0,,What?! She's dead?
Dialogue: 0,0:25:18.57,0:25:21.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Then, why didn't you tell me?\NWhy were you hiding it?!
Dialogue: 0,0:25:22.47,0:25:23.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Answer me, child.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:24.44,0:25:26.06,Default,,0,0,0,,I didn't want Setsuko to know.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:28.97,0:25:30.59,Default,,0,0,0,,So, she is dead...
Dialogue: 0,0:25:32.64,0:25:33.68,Default,,0,0,0,,How awful!
Dialogue: 0,0:25:33.92,0:25:36.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, you'd best write your father\Nand tell him!
Dialogue: 0,0:25:43.11,0:25:44.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Seita!
Dialogue: 0,0:25:45.63,0:25:47.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Look!\NShe bought me new shoes!
Dialogue: 0,0:25:49.91,0:25:51.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Good for you, Setsuko.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:52.21,0:25:53.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Hello there!
Dialogue: 0,0:25:56.33,0:25:57.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Wacth this.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:12.61,0:26:13.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't be too long.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:19.80,0:26:21.84,Default,,0,0,0,,What was making that noise?
Dialogue: 0,0:26:22.70,0:26:25.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Bullfrogs. There is\Nnothing to be scared of.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:27.01,0:26:28.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Firefly!
Dialogue: 0,0:26:35.19,0:26:36.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Ready? Come on, catch it.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:42.59,0:26:44.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Aww, you squashed it.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:45.16,0:26:46.90,Default,,0,0,0,,It smells!
Dialogue: 0,0:26:47.61,0:26:49.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't squeeze so hard next time.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:17.95,0:27:19.44,Default,,0,0,0,,There're millions of them!
Dialogue: 0,0:27:33.55,0:27:36.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey Setsuko, close your eyes\Nand say "ah."
Dialogue: 0,0:27:36.53,0:27:37.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Why should I?
Dialogue: 0,0:27:37.61,0:27:39.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Come on. Just do it. "Ah."
Dialogue: 0,0:27:51.93,0:27:53.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Fruit drop!
Dialogue: 0,0:27:54.52,0:27:58.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Orange and cherry\Nand lemon and lime!
Dialogue: 0,0:27:58.59,0:28:02.12,Default,,0,0,0,,I am eating my candy\Nand taking my time!
Dialogue: 0,0:28:08.83,0:28:11.49,Default,,0,0,0,,That was close. I\Nalmost swallowed it.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:28.08,0:28:28.50,Default,,0,0,0,,We're home.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:28.51,0:28:29.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Where were you two?
Dialogue: 0,0:28:34.51,0:28:35.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Did you thank the lady?
Dialogue: 0,0:28:36.51,0:28:37.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, ma'am.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:39.86,0:28:41.29,Default,,0,0,0,,That food looks good.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:11.39,0:29:14.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Seita. why aren't you up?\NShouldn't you be going to school?
Dialogue: 0,0:29:14.36,0:29:15.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Or something?
Dialogue: 0,0:29:16.02,0:29:20.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, but the steelworks they had me\Nworking in was bombed the other day.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:20.59,0:29:24.19,Default,,0,0,0,,And my school burned down.\NThere's no place to go.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:24.77,0:29:28.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, I hope\Nyou've written to your father.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:28.25,0:29:30.89,Default,,0,0,0,,I did that. I sent it\Nthrough the Naval Office.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:30.99,0:29:31.58,Default,,0,0,0,,When?
Dialogue: 0,0:29:32.03,0:29:35.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Just after we came here. I guess\Nit was about 10 days ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:36.56,0:29:38.40,Default,,0,0,0,,That seems strange.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:39.56,0:29:41.55,Default,,0,0,0,,There should have been\Na reply by now.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:43.27,0:29:46.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Return the scissors when you've\Nfinished with them, Setsuko.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:55.30,0:29:56.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Any news on the war?
Dialogue: 0,0:29:57.21,0:29:58.70,Default,,0,0,0,,It's beginning to look hopeless.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:00.97,0:30:04.53,Default,,0,0,0,,It seems that the more factories we lose,\Nthe harder the others have to work.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:05.07,0:30:07.35,Default,,0,0,0,,The War efforts is eating\Nup all of our supplies.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:09.52,0:30:12.64,Default,,0,0,0,,You're right. That's why food's\Ngetting so hard to find.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:15.71,0:30:18.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Our soldiers aren't the only ones\Nwho are suffering.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:21.06,0:30:23.89,Default,,0,0,0,,You work for our country's\Ndefense too, young lady.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:24.67,0:30:27.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Eat up and work\Nas hard as you can!
Dialogue: 0,0:30:35.84,0:30:36.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Not again.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:37.45,0:30:39.67,Default,,0,0,0,,So you've taken in\Na couple of homeless children?
Dialogue: 0,0:30:39.80,0:30:42.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Poor things, losing their\Nmother when they're so young.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:46.86,0:30:48.57,Default,,0,0,0,,What's wrong? You got an itch?
Dialogue: 0,0:30:48.96,0:30:52.06,Default,,0,0,0,,It's hot. I hate shelters!
Dialogue: 0,0:30:52.38,0:30:55.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Just hang on. We'll be\Nout of here soon enough.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:06.57,0:31:07.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, you wanna go to the beach?
Dialogue: 0,0:31:08.84,0:31:11.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah! Yeah! Let's go! Let's go.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:26.29,0:31:29.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Wow. It's all vegetable fields now.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:27.68,0:32:29.00,Default,,0,0,0,,What're they doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:32:29.26,0:32:30.65,Default,,0,0,0,,They are making sea salt.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:31.51,0:32:34.26,Default,,0,0,0,,It's all the salt and\Nsoy sauce is rationed.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:35.71,0:32:37.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Alright. Hurry up, Setsuko!
Dialogue: 0,0:33:07.47,0:33:08.70,Default,,0,0,0,,It might be a little cold.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:09.27,0:33:10.75,Default,,0,0,0,,It is cold!
Dialogue: 0,0:33:12.76,0:33:14.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Feels good, right?\NYou won't itch now.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:23.50,0:33:25.03,Default,,0,0,0,,It's a big bath!
Dialogue: 0,0:33:36.62,0:33:39.63,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm gonna eat you!
Dialogue: 0,0:33:39.70,0:33:40.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Here I come!
Dialogue: 0,0:34:07.17,0:34:09.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Snippy... Snippy... Snippy Crab.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:10.36,0:34:13.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Snippy... Snippy...\NSnippy...Snip.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:14.10,0:34:16.83,Default,,0,0,0,,What's wrong?\NIs he sleeping?
Dialogue: 0,0:34:26.64,0:34:27.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't look at that.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:31.05,0:34:33.42,Default,,0,0,0,,When it gets a little warmer,\NI'll teach you how to swim.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:36.30,0:34:38.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's swim, then we can eat.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:43.84,0:34:46.41,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}We'll swim,\Nand that'll make us hungry.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:34:54.77,0:34:55.80,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Seita!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:34:56.76,0:34:57.84,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Setsuko!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:34:58.57,0:35:00.06,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}You're hungry, aren't you?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:35:05.99,0:35:07.77,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}There's food here for you here.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:35:08.33,0:35:10.53,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Come on now. Time to eat.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:35:42.08,0:35:44.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Mother! How are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:35:47.40,0:35:49.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you alright, my daughter?
Dialogue: 0,0:35:49.68,0:35:51.69,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm fine, really!
Dialogue: 0,0:35:51.77,0:35:52.90,Default,,0,0,0,,They're very nice here.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:53.70,0:35:54.82,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm hungry.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:57.42,0:35:59.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's get home before we're\Ncaught in the next air raid.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:00.15,0:36:03.48,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm tired. Please carry me.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:05.81,0:36:07.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Air raid!
Dialogue: 0,0:36:18.52,0:36:22.36,Default,,0,0,0,,I am afraid these are no use. Your\Nmother won't be needing kimonos anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:22.49,0:36:24.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Why don't you trade them\Nfor rice?
Dialogue: 0,0:36:25.11,0:36:29.42,Default,,0,0,0,,I've been trading off my things\NLittle by little for food we need.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:30.66,0:36:34.07,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}You can probably get\Na full toh of rice for them.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:36:34.20,0:36:35.04,Default,,0,0,0,,That much?
Dialogue: 0,0:36:35.34,0:36:37.42,Default,,0,0,0,,You need your nourishment, you know.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:37.66,0:36:40.30,Default,,0,0,0,,I mean, how can you be a soldier\Nif you don't grow up healthy?
Dialogue: 0,0:36:41.02,0:36:42.44,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}A whole toh of rice.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:36:42.70,0:36:46.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Your mother would be glad that you\Ndidn't just let them just go to waste.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:46.86,0:36:48.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Why don't I take\Nthem for you?
Dialogue: 0,0:36:50.46,0:36:51.24,Default,,0,0,0,,No!
Dialogue: 0,0:36:51.89,0:36:53.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Have you been awake\Nthis whole time?
Dialogue: 0,0:36:53.88,0:36:54.71,Default,,0,0,0,, They're Mama's!
Dialogue: 0,0:36:54.85,0:36:58.37,Default,,0,0,0,,No, they're Mama's!\NDon't take them!
Dialogue: 0,0:36:58.70,0:37:01.77,Default,,0,0,0,,No! No! No!
Dialogue: 0,0:37:02.54,0:37:04.35,Default,,0,0,0,,- Setsuko. Let them go.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:04.97,0:37:05.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Setsuko!
Dialogue: 0,0:37:06.14,0:37:07.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Setsuko!
Dialogue: 0,0:37:07.11,0:37:11.40,Default,,0,0,0,,No.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:16.50,0:37:17.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Mama!
Dialogue: 0,0:37:18.98,0:37:21.11,Default,,0,0,0,,No!
Dialogue: 0,0:37:51.70,0:37:54.64,Default,,0,0,0,,It's fine rice.\N- Yes...
Dialogue: 0,0:37:54.94,0:37:57.44,Default,,0,0,0,,We'll have a proper\Nrice dinner tonight, Setsuko.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:01.57,0:38:03.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Here, this is your share.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:11.99,0:38:13.21,Default,,0,0,0,,White rice, Setsuko!
Dialogue: 0,0:38:24.81,0:38:25.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Here you go.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:26.72,0:38:29.28,Default,,0,0,0,,With my daughter and our lodger\Nworking so hard...
Dialogue: 0,0:38:29.57,0:38:32.83,Default,,0,0,0,,I've felt just terrible about\Nnot having rice to give them.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:35.72,0:38:38.06,Default,,0,0,0,,It's great, huh?\NReal white rice.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:41.74,0:38:42.70,Default,,0,0,0,,More please!
Dialogue: 0,0:38:43.13,0:38:44.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:48.02,0:38:51.09,Default,,0,0,0,,You're just gobbling it down\Ntonight, aren't you, Setsuko?
Dialogue: 0,0:38:51.29,0:38:53.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Uh-huh. It's very good!
Dialogue: 0,0:38:59.34,0:38:59.97,Default,,0,0,0,,What's wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:39:00.44,0:39:02.61,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't want rice porridge!
Dialogue: 0,0:39:03.64,0:39:06.14,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't suppose we have any\Nmore of those pickled plums?
Dialogue: 0,0:39:06.60,0:39:08.88,Default,,0,0,0,,No, we finished\Nthose off ages ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:10.39,0:39:11.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Here's your lunch.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:11.86,0:39:13.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Thanks. I'd better get going.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:17.68,0:39:19.16,Default,,0,0,0,, Bye, mom.\N- Take care.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:20.32,0:39:22.97,Default,,0,0,0,,We'll have rice balls for lunch.\NJust hold on until then.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:23.10,0:39:26.63,Default,,0,0,0,,You stop that! You'll have\Nporridge for lunch too!
Dialogue: 0,0:39:27.83,0:39:29.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you think\Na lazy slug like you deserves...
Dialogue: 0,0:39:29.98,0:39:33.84,Default,,0,0,0,,the same as people who are\Nworking so hard for our nation?!
Dialogue: 0,0:39:36.37,0:39:41.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Really, Seita. You're certainly old enough to\Nknow now that everyone has got to cooperate.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:42.50,0:39:47.24,Default,,0,0,0,,You keep saying you want rice, but do you\Ndo anything to earn this rice you want?
Dialogue: 0,0:39:47.41,0:39:48.76,Default,,0,0,0,,No, you don't!
Dialogue: 0,0:39:57.99,0:40:00.69,Default,,0,0,0,,I even give you some rice,\Nand you still complain!
Dialogue: 0,0:40:03.10,0:40:05.98,Default,,0,0,0,,But it was our rice in the first place.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:06.27,0:40:08.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, so now\NI'm cheating you, am I?
Dialogue: 0,0:40:09.42,0:40:13.67,Default,,0,0,0,,How dare you say that!\NAfter I take you two into my home!
Dialogue: 0,0:40:16.29,0:40:17.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Fine!
Dialogue: 0,0:40:17.14,0:40:20.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Here is a new rule. From now on,\Nwe will make our own dinners.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:20.62,0:40:22.11,Default,,0,0,0,,How do you like that?
Dialogue: 0,0:40:22.64,0:40:27.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Tell me Seita. You have other relatives\Nin Tokyo, don't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:40:27.24,0:40:29.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Some people on your mother's\Nside of the family?
Dialogue: 0,0:40:30.19,0:40:33.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Why not write to them?\NWe could be bombed any day.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:35.76,0:40:37.76,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't know where to find them.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:46.67,0:40:48.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's go home, Mommy.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:48.74,0:40:51.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Uh-huh. Daddy's waiting for us.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:53.47,0:40:57.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Frogs are singing,\Nit's time to go home
Dialogue: 0,0:41:01.55,0:41:02.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Sorry you had to wait so long.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:07.23,0:41:07.98,Default,,0,0,0,,What's wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:41:08.67,0:41:11.96,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm really hungry.\NAnd thirsty too.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:12.18,0:41:12.78,Default,,0,0,0,,OK.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:17.65,0:41:19.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Here. It's a fruit drop.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:22.99,0:41:24.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Mom has 7000 yen in the bank.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:25.13,0:41:30.47,Default,,0,0,0,,7000. That's more than enough for us\Nto live on, so don't you worry, OK?
Dialogue: 0,0:41:32.69,0:41:38.26,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm telling Dad to write back soon, because\NSetsuko's waiting. Write your name
Dialogue: 0,0:41:48.10,0:41:49.87,Default,,0,0,0,,You're in luck.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:50.97,0:41:55.38,Default,,0,0,0,,You can't buy a stove like this easily\Nnowadays. You know what I mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:41:55.82,0:41:59.99,Default,,0,0,0,,It's almost impossible to find\Nany hardware to sell.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:00.24,0:42:02.32,Default,,0,0,0,,And of this quality.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:04.27,0:42:08.26,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll take that comb, and...\NDo you have an umbrella?
Dialogue: 0,0:42:08.40,0:42:11.02,Default,,0,0,0,,An umbrella... Oh, yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:42:12.76,0:42:16.95,Default,,0,0,0,,It's raining cats and dogs.\NIt's raining cats and dogs.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:17.24,0:42:21.28,Default,,0,0,0,,But I have a raincoat and\Nmy big red rubber clods.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:21.42,0:42:25.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Drip-drop, plip-plop\NDown comes the rain!
Dialogue: 0,0:42:25.72,0:42:29.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Drip-drop, plip-plop\NDown comes the rain!
Dialogue: 0,0:42:38.20,0:42:39.35,Default,,0,0,0,,And that should do it!
Dialogue: 0,0:42:39.83,0:42:41.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Be careful with that fire.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:41.82,0:42:42.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Right.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:46.45,0:42:47.46,Default,,0,0,0,,What are they up to?
Dialogue: 0,0:42:48.35,0:42:49.90,Default,,0,0,0,,They're doing their own cooking.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:51.03,0:42:54.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, good for them! It's about time.\NMore, please.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:55.40,0:42:57.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Mom, did you ever\Nscold them again?
Dialogue: 0,0:42:58.29,0:43:00.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, and they refuse to apologize.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:00.90,0:43:04.48,Default,,0,0,0,,And that boy even bought a stove.\NJust to spite me!
Dialogue: 0,0:43:07.85,0:43:08.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Finished!
Dialogue: 0,0:43:13.11,0:43:15.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't do that.\NThat's bad manners.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:16.75,0:43:20.46,Default,,0,0,0,,We can sit any way we want to.\NDoesn't matter.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:29.81,0:43:31.37,Default,,0,0,0,,There. Rice for two.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:31.60,0:43:31.83,Default,,0,0,0,,That's it?
Dialogue: 0,0:43:32.11,0:43:34.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Yep. Next ration will be in July.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:51.43,0:43:52.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Let me!
Dialogue: 0,0:45:24.45,0:45:24.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Ready?
Dialogue: 0,0:45:34.67,0:45:35.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Here.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:39.13,0:45:40.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you like it?
Dialogue: 0,0:45:47.42,0:45:49.14,Default,,0,0,0,,It's all different tastes!
Dialogue: 0,0:45:50.29,0:45:53.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Grape, strawberry, mint, melon.\N All the flavors are in there.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:54.36,0:45:55.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Now, drink it all up, OK?
Dialogue: 0,0:46:05.81,0:46:07.07,Default,,0,0,0,,It's all gone.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:12.10,0:46:15.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Great. They left the\Ndishes for me to do.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:16.25,0:46:17.11,Default,,0,0,0,,So selfish.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:17.39,0:46:21.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Honestly! Those little brats are two\Nof the worst children in the world.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:23.27,0:46:24.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Not again!
Dialogue: 0,0:46:26.09,0:46:30.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Seita please, that man and my daughter work\Nhard for our nation all day long.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:30.95,0:46:33.74,Default,,0,0,0,,We can't have her crying\Nkeeping them awake.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:34.18,0:46:38.51,Default,,0,0,0,,We're having enough trouble getting\Nany sleep with all of these air raids!
Dialogue: 0,0:47:05.77,0:47:10.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Attention! Attention! Report\Nfrom Central Military Division.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:11.12,0:47:13.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Several waves of\Nenemy bombers are approaching.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:14.15,0:47:16.44,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Going to the shelter again, Seita?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:47:16.76,0:47:20.49,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}You're old enough to\Nhelp fight the fires, aren't you?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:47:33.82,0:47:38.81,Default,,0,0,0,,I want to go home.\NI hate living with her!
Dialogue: 0,0:47:40.83,0:47:42.88,Default,,0,0,0,,We don't have a house\Nto go back to.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:49.48,0:47:55.90,Default,,0,0,0,,With a great big streamer shaped\Nlike a carp in the wind...
Dialogue: 0,0:47:56.15,0:47:56.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Go.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:56.98,0:48:03.76,Default,,0,0,0,,With a great big streamer shaped\Nlike a carp in the wind...
Dialogue: 0,0:48:04.60,0:48:11.08,Default,,0,0,0,,The big one's Papa, and\Nthe little one's the kids.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:11.09,0:48:11.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Stop it!
Dialogue: 0,0:48:12.99,0:48:16.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't you realize that\Nthere's a war going on?!
Dialogue: 0,0:48:16.88,0:48:18.88,Default,,0,0,0,,You two are nothing\Nbut trouble for me!
Dialogue: 0,0:48:19.18,0:48:21.60,Default,,0,0,0,,A couple of pests,\Nthat's what you are!
Dialogue: 0,0:48:21.89,0:48:25.68,Default,,0,0,0,,You're no help during the raids.Take!\NTake! Take!
Dialogue: 0,0:48:25.94,0:48:29.44,Default,,0,0,0,,You could go live in that\Nshelter for all I care!
Dialogue: 0,0:48:34.06,0:48:34.89,Default,,0,0,0,,That's it.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:36.81,0:48:37.95,Default,,0,0,0,,We can live here.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:40.42,0:48:43.95,Default,,0,0,0,,No one seems to be using it.\NIt seems sturdy enough.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:44.31,0:48:46.06,Default,,0,0,0,, And we can live\Njust like we want to.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:46.33,0:48:48.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Can we live here really?!
Dialogue: 0,0:49:12.90,0:49:15.96,Default,,0,0,0,,We've bothered you long enough.\NWe should be leaving now.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:16.29,0:49:18.26,Default,,0,0,0,,You are leaving? For where?
Dialogue: 0,0:49:18.75,0:49:20.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Haven't really decided yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:23.46,0:49:25.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Well then, you two, bye bye.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:25.96,0:49:27.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Take care of yourselves.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:47.57,0:49:49.44,Default,,0,0,0,,And this'll be the kitchen!
Dialogue: 0,0:49:52.06,0:49:54.41,Default,,0,0,0,,And this'll be the front door!
Dialogue: 0,0:49:56.38,0:49:58.37,Default,,0,0,0,,But where's the bathroom, Seita?
Dialogue: 0,0:50:00.49,0:50:03.34,Default,,0,0,0,,That can be anywhere.\NYou wanna go somewhere with me?
Dialogue: 0,0:50:13.07,0:50:14.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Thanks a lot. Where do\Nyou want the wagon?
Dialogue: 0,0:50:15.73,0:50:17.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Just leave it right there.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:19.52,0:50:23.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you think you can sell my\Nsister and I a little bit of food,
Dialogue: 0,0:50:23.66,0:50:25.28,Default,,0,0,0,,and maybe a bail of straw?
Dialogue: 0,0:50:25.30,0:50:28.35,Default,,0,0,0,,I guess so.\NThere's not much left, though.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:23.27,0:51:25.23,Default,,0,0,0,,- It smells so good!\N- Let's eat.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:53.84,0:51:56.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, I guess we can always\Neat frogs if we have to.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:56.35,0:51:57.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Frogs?
Dialogue: 0,0:51:57.68,0:51:59.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah. They taste great.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:02.97,0:52:04.86,Default,,0,0,0,,You'd better get under\Nthe mosquito net now.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:15.71,0:52:16.38,Default,,0,0,0,,What's wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:52:16.85,0:52:18.74,Default,,0,0,0,,I forgot my toothbrush.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:18.86,0:52:20.39,Default,,0,0,0,,One night without it\Nwon't matter.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:24.98,0:52:27.94,Default,,0,0,0,,It's getting pretty buggy out here.\NYou'd better go get under the net.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:28.44,0:52:30.42,Default,,0,0,0,,It's dark in there. I'm scared.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:36.73,0:52:38.64,Default,,0,0,0,,I have to pee, Setsuko.\NHow about you?
Dialogue: 0,0:52:44.15,0:52:45.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Look, a kamikaze.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:47.35,0:52:49.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Looks like a firefly.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:49.31,0:52:49.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:52.02,0:52:53.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, let's catch some.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:55.26,0:52:56.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay, get in.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:04.11,0:53:04.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Ready?
Dialogue: 0,0:53:10.91,0:53:12.17,Default,,0,0,0,,I can see you!
Dialogue: 0,0:53:12.91,0:53:14.17,Default,,0,0,0,,I can see you, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:18.34,0:53:19.29,Default,,0,0,0,,A hair clip.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:24.19,0:53:26.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, let's get\Nas many as we can!
Dialogue: 0,0:54:21.63,0:54:25.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Did I ever tell you I went to see a naval\Nreview one time, just before you were born.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:26.27,0:54:27.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Naval review?
Dialogue: 0,0:54:27.88,0:54:30.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah. Dad's naval cruiser\Nwas named the Maya.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:30.81,0:54:33.06,Default,,0,0,0,,It was in formation with the\Nfleet in the harbor.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:10.31,0:55:13.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Mighty fortresses\Nfloating on the seas!
Dialogue: 0,0:55:14.06,0:55:18.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Defending our homeland\Nfrom invaders near and far!
Dialogue: 0,0:55:18.30,0:55:19.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Enemy plane!
Dialogue: 0,0:55:31.28,0:55:33.73,Default,,0,0,0,,I wonder where Dad is\Nfighting right about now.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:03.49,0:56:05.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Get off of me, Seita...
Dialogue: 0,0:56:44.96,0:56:45.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Whatcha doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:56:45.89,0:56:49.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Making a grave.\NMama's in a grave too.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:56.01,0:56:58.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Auntie told me about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:59.16,0:57:03.59,Default,,0,0,0,,She said that Mama died, and\Nthat she's in a grave now.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:34.19,0:57:36.14,Default,,0,0,0,,We'll go and visit\Nher grave sometime.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:36.88,0:57:40.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you remember the graveyard, Setsuko?\NThat really pretty one out near Nunobiki?
Dialogue: 0,0:57:42.47,0:57:47.55,Default,,0,0,0,,That's where she is now. Resting\Npeacefully Under a big camphor tree.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:47.73,0:57:50.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Why do fireflies\Nhave to die so soon?
Dialogue: 0,0:58:28.73,0:58:31.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Wow, looks like someone\Nis living in here.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:31.51,0:58:33.28,Default,,0,0,0,,They probably lost their house.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:34.34,0:58:36.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Maybe it's some crazy hermit.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:38.40,0:58:39.59,Default,,0,0,0,,It's a swing.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:39.78,0:58:42.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, a kid lives here.\NWhat's this?
Dialogue: 0,0:58:42.96,0:58:44.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Rest in Peace! Rest in Peace!
Dialogue: 0,0:58:47.67,0:58:49.26,Default,,0,0,0,,I wish it was real food.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:50.74,0:58:52.98,Default,,0,0,0,,It says "Setsuko".\NWho's Setsuko?
Dialogue: 0,0:58:53.11,0:58:55.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Look guys! Dried out frog guts!
Dialogue: 0,0:58:55.69,0:58:57.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Who'd wanna eat that?!
Dialogue: 0,0:58:57.62,0:58:59.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Nobody I know\Nwould ever eat this stuff!
Dialogue: 0,0:59:02.98,0:59:04.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Ground soybeans!
Dialogue: 0,0:59:06.16,0:59:08.17,Default,,0,0,0,,And I thought\Nthe food I got was bad!
Dialogue: 0,0:59:08.22,0:59:09.78,Default,,0,0,0,,A ghost! A ghost!
Dialogue: 0,0:59:14.64,0:59:17.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait up! hey! Wait up!
Dialogue: 0,0:59:22.91,0:59:25.70,Default,,0,0,0,,I've traded everything for rice.\NEven my mom's kimono.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:25.84,0:59:27.44,Default,,0,0,0,,There's nothing left to trade.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:28.00,0:59:30.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Please, I can pay you\Ngood money for the rice.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:32.24,0:59:35.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Sorry. I can't trade\Nor sell anything to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:36.09,0:59:39.76,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm a farmer, but I'm afraid even\NI don't have any rice to share.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:47.28,0:59:49.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't you have other\Nrelatives to help you?
Dialogue: 0,0:59:49.63,0:59:51.49,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't know how to\Ncontact any of them.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:51.91,0:59:55.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Then take my advice and just go\Nback to the woman in the village.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:56.18,0:59:58.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Look, everything's rationed now.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:59.35,1:00:01.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Can't survive outside\Nof the system.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:02.73,1:00:05.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Just swallow your pride\Nand apologize to her.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:11.67,1:00:14.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Thanks, anyway. I'll just\Ngo and ask someone else.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:16.71,1:00:20.52,Default,,0,0,0,,You're the son of a navy man, aren't you?\NSo, try to be brave.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:25.50,1:00:26.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Look out!
Dialogue: 0,1:00:52.13,1:00:53.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Is it good?
Dialogue: 0,1:01:33.92,1:01:34.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh no!
Dialogue: 0,1:02:35.90,1:02:37.49,Default,,0,0,0,,It doesn't matter\Nif you like it or not.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:37.66,1:02:38.35,Default,,0,0,0,,You have to eat!
Dialogue: 0,1:02:38.88,1:02:40.91,Default,,0,0,0,,You need to, so you\Ncan grow up strong!
Dialogue: 0,1:02:43.32,1:02:44.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Seita...
Dialogue: 0,1:02:46.22,1:02:50.41,Default,,0,0,0,,I feel-My insides\Nfeel really funny.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:51.17,1:02:52.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you cold?
Dialogue: 0,1:02:52.87,1:02:56.01,Default,,0,0,0,,I've been having diarrhea.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:01.34,1:03:02.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey you...!
Dialogue: 0,1:03:04.49,1:03:05.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey! Sorry!
Dialogue: 0,1:03:05.93,1:03:08.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Sorry! I didn't mean to!\NForgive me!
Dialogue: 0,1:03:10.52,1:03:14.04,Default,,0,0,0,,My sister's sick. I just wanted\Nto get her some sugar! I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:14.11,1:03:18.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, sure! Stealing food's\Na serious crime in wartime!
Dialogue: 0,1:03:19.22,1:03:23.60,Default,,0,0,0,,You god damned...!\NCome back here!
Dialogue: 0,1:03:34.64,1:03:36.75,Default,,0,0,0,,What the hell?!\NPotatoes too?!
Dialogue: 0,1:03:36.89,1:03:39.57,Default,,0,0,0,,So, you're the one who's\Nbeen stealing my crops!
Dialogue: 0,1:03:39.66,1:03:42.66,Default,,0,0,0,,- I'm sorry!\N- Seita...
Dialogue: 0,1:03:44.42,1:03:46.31,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll never do it again, I swear!
Dialogue: 0,1:03:46.34,1:03:47.79,Default,,0,0,0,,I promise you will\Nnever see me again.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:47.96,1:03:50.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Tell that to the cops!\NI'll take you there myself!
Dialogue: 0,1:03:51.45,1:03:54.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Now walk! I hope they lock you\Nup for the rest of the war!
Dialogue: 0,1:03:54.33,1:03:55.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Seita...\N- Please, she's sick!
Dialogue: 0,1:03:55.41,1:03:57.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Seita!\N- She needs me! No!
Dialogue: 0,1:03:57.97,1:03:58.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Move!
Dialogue: 0,1:03:58.68,1:04:03.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Seita!
Dialogue: 0,1:04:05.70,1:04:07.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Seita...
Dialogue: 0,1:04:07.72,1:04:08.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Seita...
Dialogue: 0,1:04:14.54,1:04:18.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Based on what you both told me, the\Nnature of the crime is very clear.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:18.64,1:04:22.41,Default,,0,0,0,,So I thank you for the information, sir.\NI will take care of this. You may go now.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:22.56,1:04:23.52,Default,,0,0,0,,But, officer...
Dialogue: 0,1:04:24.91,1:04:27.06,Default,,0,0,0,,You've knocked\Nthis poor kid around enough.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:29.19,1:04:30.86,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm even tempted to call it...
Dialogue: 0,1:04:32.45,1:04:33.60,Default,,0,0,0,,...assault!
Dialogue: 0,1:04:33.85,1:04:35.90,Default,,0,0,0,,I... er... Thank you, sir!
Dialogue: 0,1:04:39.86,1:04:42.41,Default,,0,0,0,,I suppose you have heard\Nabout the latest attack.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:45.20,1:04:48.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Would you like a glass\Nof water or something,son?
Dialogue: 0,1:04:58.11,1:04:59.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Setsuko.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:07.82,1:05:08.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Seita!
Dialogue: 0,1:05:25.70,1:05:26.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Seita.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:34.03,1:05:38.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Should I get a doctor for you, Seita?\NWhat parts hurt? I can help you.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:45.32,1:05:46.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Setsuko!
Dialogue: 0,1:05:54.98,1:05:58.27,Default,,0,0,0,,I have to go to the bathroom..
Dialogue: 0,1:06:01.81,1:06:03.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Can it wait a little bit?
Dialogue: 0,1:06:05.08,1:06:05.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Hop on.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:14.27,1:06:20.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Daddy is gone to the mountain\Nto bring back some firewood...
Dialogue: 0,1:06:30.90,1:06:32.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Hurry! Come on!
Dialogue: 0,1:07:10.16,1:07:11.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Setsuko. Dinner.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:15.36,1:07:19.59,Default,,0,0,0,,This pumpkin's great.\NTastes like sweet bean jelly.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:20.79,1:07:23.12,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't like that stuff.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:23.37,1:07:26.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Look, if you don't eat,\NDad' will blame me for it.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:26.79,1:07:31.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Come on, ready? I'll even help you, OK?\NNow come on. Cheer up and eat!
Dialogue: 0,1:07:34.32,1:07:37.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Once you are better, I'll take you to\Nthe beach again, Setsuko.I promise.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:19.99,1:08:22.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah! Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,1:09:14.63,1:09:16.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Now I'll really get you\Nsomething good to eat, Setsuko!
Dialogue: 0,1:09:27.44,1:09:28.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Seita...
Dialogue: 0,1:09:35.10,1:09:36.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Seita...
Dialogue: 0,1:09:38.25,1:09:41.60,Default,,0,0,0,,So, you are telling me these\Nwere your mother's? Oh, please.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:41.79,1:09:45.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Try to pawn your garbage off on me?\NGet out of here.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:55.43,1:09:56.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Setsuko.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:57.86,1:09:58.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Setsuko!
Dialogue: 0,1:10:25.96,1:10:26.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Setsuko.
Dialogue: 0,1:10:34.67,1:10:38.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Seita... Water...
Dialogue: 0,1:10:41.28,1:10:42.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah...
Dialogue: 0,1:10:49.22,1:10:50.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Breathe in.
Dialogue: 0,1:10:50.83,1:10:51.76,Default,,0,0,0,,And out.
Dialogue: 0,1:10:56.05,1:10:58.23,Default,,0,0,0,,She's been having diarrhea\Nfor a while now.
Dialogue: 0,1:10:58.93,1:11:01.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Prickly heat and rashes\Nall over her body.
Dialogue: 0,1:11:01.81,1:11:04.51,Default,,0,0,0,,And her skin seems very\Nsensitive to any salt water.
Dialogue: 0,1:11:07.42,1:11:11.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Weakening from malnutrition. It's typical.\NProbably due to the diarrhea.
Dialogue: 0,1:11:12.63,1:11:13.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Next patient?
Dialogue: 0,1:11:13.62,1:11:15.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Can you give her\Nmedicine or a shot?
Dialogue: 0,1:11:16.48,1:11:18.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't wanna shot.
Dialogue: 0,1:11:18.61,1:11:21.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Please, doctor, you have to help her!\NMedicine, please.
Dialogue: 0,1:11:21.64,1:11:27.39,Default,,0,0,0,,GIve her some medicine? All this child\Nneeds is some food. A good meal.
Dialogue: 0,1:11:27.55,1:11:28.88,Default,,0,0,0,,She needs food...
Dialogue: 0,1:11:29.67,1:11:30.67,Default,,0,0,0,,How can I help you?
Dialogue: 0,1:11:31.18,1:11:33.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Where am I supposed\Nto get food?!
Dialogue: 0,1:12:22.17,1:12:26.50,Default,,0,0,0,,I am so hungry. What\Ndo you want to eat?
Dialogue: 0,1:12:26.73,1:12:31.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Tempura, sashimi, jelly...
Dialogue: 0,1:12:32.48,1:12:33.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Anything else?
Dialogue: 0,1:12:33.77,1:12:35.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Ice cream.
Dialogue: 0,1:12:36.37,1:12:37.70,Default,,0,0,0,,And also...
Dialogue: 0,1:12:38.51,1:12:40.34,Default,,0,0,0,,I want fruit drops.
Dialogue: 0,1:12:40.97,1:12:43.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Fruit drops? Okay!
Dialogue: 0,1:12:47.53,1:12:50.89,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll withdraw all the money and\Nbuy you all the food you need.
Dialogue: 0,1:12:51.50,1:12:55.97,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't want anything.\NYou can have it.
Dialogue: 0,1:12:56.96,1:13:02.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't go! Stay with me!\NDon't leave me alone!
Dialogue: 0,1:13:02.98,1:13:04.77,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't want you\Nto worry, Setsuko.
Dialogue: 0,1:13:05.84,1:13:09.02,Default,,0,0,0,,I am going to go buy you some\Ngood nourishing food, OK?
Dialogue: 0,1:13:10.44,1:13:15.31,Default,,0,0,0,,And I'll never... I will never\Never leave you again. Never, ever.
Dialogue: 0,1:13:17.65,1:13:18.77,Default,,0,0,0,,I promise.
Dialogue: 0,1:13:41.27,1:13:42.49,Default,,0,0,0,,3000 yen.
Dialogue: 0,1:13:42.61,1:13:44.38,Default,,0,0,0,,There's a typhoon coming?
Dialogue: 0,1:13:44.66,1:13:46.48,Default,,0,0,0,,That's just typical, isn't it?
Dialogue: 0,1:13:46.64,1:13:49.88,Default,,0,0,0,,We get our "divine\Nwind" after we surrender. Figures...
Dialogue: 0,1:13:49.97,1:13:52.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Surrender? Are you saying\Nwe've lost the war?!
Dialogue: 0,1:13:53.42,1:13:55.35,Default,,0,0,0,,So, you haven't\Nheard, young man?
Dialogue: 0,1:13:59.19,1:14:02.61,Default,,0,0,0,,You are telling me Japan's lost the war?\NThe Great Japanese Empire?
Dialogue: 0,1:14:02.65,1:14:03.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,1:14:03.38,1:14:05.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Surrendered unconditionally.
Dialogue: 0,1:14:07.13,1:14:08.22,Default,,0,0,0,,But what about the fleet?\NAre they...
Dialogue: 0,1:14:08.38,1:14:09.62,Default,,0,0,0,,All gone.
Dialogue: 0,1:14:10.17,1:14:13.60,Default,,0,0,0,,The whole fleet's been sent to the\Nbottom of the sea. Not one left afloat.
Dialogue: 0,1:14:13.84,1:14:14.37,Default,,0,0,0,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,1:14:14.50,1:14:16.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Was my Dad's ship sunk, too?! Do you know?
Dialogue: 0,1:14:16.66,1:14:18.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Please tell me. Is that why\Nhe hasn't written me back?
Dialogue: 0,1:14:19.53,1:14:21.17,Default,,0,0,0,,How the hell should I know?
Dialogue: 0,1:14:22.57,1:14:23.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Crazy kid.
Dialogue: 0,1:14:28.52,1:14:29.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Damn him.
Dialogue: 0,1:14:29.96,1:14:31.02,Default,,0,0,0,,God damn him.
Dialogue: 0,1:14:46.07,1:14:48.04,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm so hungry.
Dialogue: 0,1:14:53.43,1:14:54.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Daddy.
Dialogue: 0,1:15:02.21,1:15:03.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Now Dad's gone too.
Dialogue: 0,1:15:05.68,1:15:06.71,Default,,0,0,0,,He's dead too.
Dialogue: 0,1:15:09.89,1:15:10.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Dad...
Dialogue: 0,1:15:54.43,1:15:58.85,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry that I'm so late, Setsuko. I'll\Ngo ahead and start making up some rice.
Dialogue: 0,1:15:59.41,1:16:01.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Up they go.
Dialogue: 0,1:16:03.37,1:16:06.05,Default,,0,0,0,,And down again.
Dialogue: 0,1:16:08.22,1:16:10.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh. The firefly's stopped.
Dialogue: 0,1:16:11.28,1:16:13.65,Default,,0,0,0,,I bought us some chicken\Nand I got a few eggs.
Dialogue: 0,1:16:15.98,1:16:17.12,Default,,0,0,0,,And I also have...
Dialogue: 0,1:16:26.17,1:16:28.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Setsuko, what's in your mouth?
Dialogue: 0,1:16:32.69,1:16:35.24,Default,,0,0,0,,This is a marble.\NIt isn't a drop!
Dialogue: 0,1:16:37.84,1:16:41.76,Default,,0,0,0,,I brought you something really special.\NI know that you are goning to like it.
Dialogue: 0,1:16:45.33,1:16:48.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Seita...Have one.
Dialogue: 0,1:16:52.29,1:16:54.22,Default,,0,0,0,,One what, Setsuko?
Dialogue: 0,1:16:55.30,1:16:56.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Rice balls.
Dialogue: 0,1:16:58.59,1:17:00.51,Default,,0,0,0,,I made them for you.
Dialogue: 0,1:17:00.74,1:17:01.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Here...
Dialogue: 0,1:17:03.29,1:17:06.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Here, have- have one.
Dialogue: 0,1:17:10.82,1:17:12.96,Default,,0,0,0,,You don't want them?
Dialogue: 0,1:17:13.37,1:17:14.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Setsuko!
Dialogue: 0,1:17:24.36,1:17:27.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Look here. Watermelon.\NAnd I didn't steal it.
Dialogue: 0,1:17:40.14,1:17:41.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Here, eat it.
Dialogue: 0,1:17:50.21,1:17:51.88,Default,,0,0,0,,It's good...
Dialogue: 0,1:17:56.41,1:17:59.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Hold on to this and I'll go make\Nus some rice gruel with eggs.
Dialogue: 0,1:18:07.70,1:18:09.55,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll leave the melon here for you.
Dialogue: 0,1:18:11.81,1:18:12.58,Default,,0,0,0,,OK?
Dialogue: 0,1:18:13.88,1:18:15.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Seita...
Dialogue: 0,1:18:16.64,1:18:17.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,1:18:42.86,1:18:44.62,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}She never woke up.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,1:19:38.60,1:19:41.13,Default,,0,0,0,,There you go.\NCharcoal for the cremation.
Dialogue: 0,1:19:41.46,1:19:45.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Now, since it's a little child, you\Nreally should do it at a temple.
Dialogue: 0,1:19:45.90,1:19:49.94,Default,,0,0,0,,About the body, it should be lightly \Ndressed and use beanstalks for a good fire.
Dialogue: 0,1:19:51.15,1:19:53.99,Default,,0,0,0,,In spite of it all,\Nit's a lovely day.
Dialogue: 0,1:20:01.39,1:20:02.85,Default,,0,0,0,,It's so good to be home!
Dialogue: 0,1:20:03.82,1:20:05.34,Default,,0,0,0,,It hasn't changed a bit.
Dialogue: 0,1:20:08.35,1:20:10.04,Default,,0,0,0,,The old phonograph.
Dialogue: 0,1:20:13.39,1:20:15.02,Default,,0,0,0,,I've missed this view.
Dialogue: 0,1:21:03.53,1:21:05.13,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Come back soon!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,1:24:43.12,1:24:46.14,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}The next morning,\NI put some of Setsuko's ashes into...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,1:24:46.27,1:24:49.26,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}...the candy tin,\Nand then climbed down the hill.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,1:24:50.17,1:24:52.44,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I never went back to the shelter.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,1:24:59.56,1:25:01.08,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Seita...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,1:25:18.30,1:25:20.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Time for bed. OK?